EN: They are proud of winning gold medals for their country.

ZH: 我们骄傲地宣布这一伟大的成就。
EN: We proudly announce this great achievement.

ZH: 她的骄傲与自信让她在工作中脱颖而出。
EN: Her pride and confidence help her stand out at work.

ZH: 这座雄伟的建筑是我们城市的骄傲。
EN: This magnificent building is the pride of our city.

